node.text: Super excited to share -The Christina Collection Flooring is starting to get racks in stores!! It will start rolling out today and  I can’t wait for you guys to get your hands on the flooring. There are 21 different colors available and the collection will be sold through our dealers in stores throughout the USA … Head to @christinacollectionflooring or the website link in my bio (www.christinacollectionflooring.com) to see pictures of the flooring samples and inquire to find a dealer near you. The flooring is extremely durable and gorgeous. I know you will love it as much as I do ❤️

node.text: All new episode of Christina On The Coast tonight! I get to do my good friend / neighbor’s home after they just moved to Newport Beach from North Carolina. Kristin got me through my summer of 2020 with some surfing, vacations with the kids and lots of girl time 🍷. And their master bathroom came out pretty amazing too 😉 ! Tune in at 9 pm or catch it on @discoveryplus ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Christina Haack on August 03, 2021. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text:
Summer nights with my number 1️⃣. ❤️

I normally turn off comments with Josh and will continue to do so if people are rude. I don’t want to waste any mins of my life blocking negative people. 

People are way too concerned about other people’s lives. 
They spend so much time judging others to avoid working on their own shit. 

Judgment is like a mirror - what we dislike in others is what we dislike in ourself. 
What I’ve seen in my life so far is when people spew hatred at me or anyone else for that matter those people are always the ones who have the most self hatred and the ones who truly need healing and self love.  Life is short. Do what you love with the ones you love. For me, that’s Josh, my kids and a few close friends and co-workers. ✌🏼

node.text:
Ride or Die. 
Some people are lucky enough to get forever the first time but no one should be shamed for things not working out and no one knows what goes on behind closed doors - remember that before making judgements and assumptions… and this woman / mama is still lucky enough to have this man choose me. ❤️
